title: Dakine Annie Boulanger Womens Team Heli Pro 18L
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2014 Annie Boulanger Womens Team Heli Pro 18L.
Features: 
- Contoured harness designed specifically to fit a woman's frame
- Vertical snowboard carry
- Diagonal ski carry
- Fleece lined goggle pocket
- Laptop sleeve
- Fits most 14" laptops
- Hydration compatible
- Organizer pocket
- Integrated rescue whistle/sternum strap
- Padded waist belt
